S.FORM: I 1945 a miheca saka 9 folad saka 1 a romi'ad masofoc ci Abdrabbuh Mansur Hadi , malamikomoday a tamdaw. O Sawara'an no kitakit no Yemen anini i ci Abdrabbuh Mansur Hadi, patirengan a romi'ad i 2012 a miheca saka 2 folad saka 27 a romi'ad.
